s:7:"#856262";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1306335;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1306335";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:14:"Admiral_Crunch";s:4:"text";s:257:"When people have raffles normally the idea is that you pay for a ticket. In this case instead of asking people to pay for a &quot;Chance&quot; to win a spot instead I suggested that people who wish to participate send in information to be randomly selected.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1427356332";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14273563353";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1306336;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1306336";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:14:"Admiral_Crunch";s:4:"text";s:184:"This was my way of making it fair given especially to how much Sali wished to charge for each slot to be fully rendered and the time it will take to put it all together with background";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1427356379";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14273563816";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1306337;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1306337";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:14:"Admiral_Crunch";s:4:"text";s:67:"This has nothing to do about my [i]ego[/i] as you had accused me of";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1427356404";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14273564071";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1306338;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1306338";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:14:"Admiral_Crunch";s:4:"text";s:210:"Hell I paid the initial cost to get the mock up YCH advert made and all of this was because I wanted to help Sali raise some money for himself knowing about his Oral surgery which he is just now recovering from";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1427356468";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14273564711";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1306341;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1306341";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:14:"Admiral_Crunch";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"551";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:2:"15";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Regulus";s:4:"text";s:488:"You are holding a raffle. Where the &#039;prize&#039; is a chance to be in your picture with your character, for the price of a normal commission anyway. So yes, I do think it takes a bit of ego to think being in a picture boning Scarlet is enough of a privilege that it qualifies as a prize. But you&#039;re not wrong that there&#039;s probably demand for it to work, which I think is kinda worse. I mean I&#039;m glad for Sali getting money, I&#039;m always in favor of that. But damn. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1427356589";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f33f1c";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14273565946";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#856262";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1306344;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1306344";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:14:"Admiral_Crunch";s:4:"text";s:117:"Let me pull back a bit and ask you a question. Do you have a problem with me using my image to help Sali raise funds?";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1427356836";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14273568390";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1306346;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1306346";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:14:"Admiral_Crunch";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"551";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:2:"15";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Regulus";s:4:"text";s:358:"I literally said my entire opinion on it. It has nothing to do with Sali, I would be saying this no matter the artist ~or~ the price. And you can do what you want. But that doesn&#039;t mean I don&#039;t think it takes a hell of an ego to give the chance to pay to be in a picture with Scarlet as a &#039;prize&#039;. It&#039;s pretty over the top, I think. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1427356963";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f33f1c";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14273569682";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#856262";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1306347;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1306347";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:14:"Admiral_Crunch";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"551";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:2:"15";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Regulus";s:4:"text";s:239:"I&#039;m happy for Sali to have all the success, and if I honestly believed anybody gave a **** about my opinion anyway, I probably would&#039;ve withheld my honesty rather than risk turning people away from potentially commissioning him. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1427357004";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f33f1c";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14273570089";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#856262";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1306348;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1306348";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:14:"Admiral_Crunch";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"551";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:2:"15";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Regulus";s:4:"text";s:81:"But it&#039;s not about that. It&#039;s literally just as simple as what I said. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1427357021";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f33f1c";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14273570258";s:15:"chat_tex